overview: SHIMMER Volume 17 features a main event of The Dangerous Angels vs. Cheerleader Melissa & MsChif, which many fans consider to be one of the best tag team bouts in SHIMMER history! Plus “The Croatian Panther” Wesna Busic makes her SHIMMER debut against Mercedes Martinez, Lacey takes on Sarah Stock, and more!
title: SHIMMER Women Athletes Volume 17
